Your server needs to _expose_ the header as part of its CORS configuration, using `WithExposedHeaders`. Here&#39;s an example:

    services
        .AddCors(options =&gt;
        {
            options.AddPolicy(CorsAllowAllOrigins, builder =&gt; 
                builder.WithOrigins(&quot;*&quot;)
                       .WithHeaders(&quot;*&quot;)
                       .WithMethods(&quot;*&quot;)
                       .WithExposedHeaders(&quot;Content-Disposition&quot;));
        });

This sets the [Access-Control-Expose-Headers](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Expose-Headers) header.

